Package: roadrunner
Title: Fast, Low-Dependency Machine Learning Algorithms
Version: 0.0.0.9028
Authors@R:
    person("Jack", "Trametta", , "jtrametta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of fast, low-dependency implementations of
    classical machine learning algorithms. The first algorithm is
    'ares()', a Multivariate Adaptive Regression Splines (MARS) fitter
    using Friedman's (1991) fast least-squares forward selection and a
    parallelized knot search built on 'Rcpp' and 'RcppParallel'.
    Additional algorithms will be added as separate exported functions
    under the same package roof.
